        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 15:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), i.e., we are conscious of them; and our misdeeds, we know them\" (ידענוּם for ידענון, as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
